headline: 3 High-Yield Dividend Stocks Perfect For Baby Boomers
summary: Baby boomers, who were born between 1946 and 1964, will be 62 to 80 years of age in 2026. Sometimes referred to as “boomers,” this cohort will often face unique financial challenges in the coming years.
